!!!html
html
    head
        meta(charset="utf-8")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
        title Geoproxy
        
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="/static/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="/static/geoproxy.css")
    body
        .row
            .col-1.col-sm-1.col-lg-2
            form(action="/", method="post").form-inline.form-horizontal.col-10.col-sm-10.col-lg-8
                legend.page-header
                    h1 Geoproxy 
                        small All the hip geospatial formats
                .row.form-group
                    .col-lg-12
                        input#url(name="url", type="url", placeholder="Service or Dataset URL Goes Here").form-control
                .row.form-group
                    label.col-lg-3.col-sm-3.col-4.control-label Input Format:
                    .btn-group#inputs(data-toggle="buttons").col-lg-9.col-sm-9
                        each input in inputs
                            .btn.btn-success
                                input(type="radio", name="inFormat", id="input-" + input, value= input)
                                = input
    
                .row.form-group
                    label.col-lg-3.col-sm-3.col-4.control-label Output Format: 
                    .btn-group#outputs(data-toggle="buttons").col-lg-9.col-sm-9
                        each output in outputs
                            .btn.btn-info
                                input(type="radio", name="outFormat", id="output-" + output, value= output)
                                = output
                
                .row.form-group
                    .col-lg-2.col-sm-2.col-2
                    .col-lg-8.col-sm-8.col-8
                        input(type="submit").btn.btn-primary.btn-block.btn-large Submit
                    .col-lg-2.col-sm-2.col-2
        
        hr        

        .row
            .col-1.col-sm-1.col-lg-2
            .col-10.col-sm-10.col-lg-8
                h2.pull-right ...does what?
        .row
            .col-1.col-sm-1.col-lg-2
            .col-10.col-sm-10.col-lg-8
                p.lead It helps convert online geospatial data from one format to another.
        .row
            .col-1.col-sm-1.col-lg-2
            .col-10.col-sm-10.col-lg-8
                h2.pull-right ...can be used as a service?
        .row
            .col-1.col-sm-1.col-lg-2
            .col-10.col-sm-10.col-lg-8
                p.lead Yes. <strong>POST</strong> something like this to 
                    code http://geoproxy.worbly.org

                pre
                    | {
                    |   "url": "http://server.com/some/data",
                    |   "inFormat": "EsriJSON",
                    |   "outFormat": "TopoJSON"
                    | }                
                p Make sure to set the header: 
                    code Content-type: application/json
                    
        hr
        
        footer
            ul
                li: a(href="https://github.com/rclark/geoproxy") On GitHub
                li Â·
                li: a(href="https://twitter.com/worbly") On Twitter
            
                
        script(src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.10.1.min.js")
        script(src="/static/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js")